    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and the air conditioning still function properly. Mechanically, the car runs and drives fine, but it does have a slow oil leak and will likely need new brake pads and tires within the next few thousand miles. It has been regularly serviced, and I have the records available for your review.",
