      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty has been pampered since day one and is in absolutely flawless shape. It drives like a dream and is seriously ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a great new home. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
