    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical mechanical preventative maintenance has been proactively addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with upgraded bolts, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution. Finished in a mirror-like coat with a pristine interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated, high-revving longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
